description: The 80-year-old was airlifted to hospital with serious injuries but died later in hospital.
title: Man, 80, dies after car plunges off cliff on the Isle of Man
title_page: Man, 80, dies after car plunges off cliff on the Isle of Man - BBC News
maintext: An 80-year-old man has died after his car plunged off a cliff and crashed onto a beach, police on the Isle of Man have said.
